To trace fluorescent beads in an unbiased manner, we developed a software toolkit in MATLAB (Mathworks, Natwick, MA). In our approach, beads are detected via multiple-scale Laplacian of Gaussian (LoG) filters104 as follows:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
